headline: Capstone Partners Announces Newly Formed Buy-Side M&A Advisory Group
summary: Capstone Partners, a leading middle market investment banking firm, announces the launch of its newly formed Buy-Side M&A Advisory Group (the Group). Kaity Templin recently joined the firm as a Director on its Sponsor Coverage Team to oversee the development of the function.
